THE VIDEO DESCRIBES THE LIFE OF A FAMILY WHO IS POOR.
THE YOUNG BOY IN THE VIDEO THOUGHT HE WAS RICH, BUT IT TURNS OUT HE WAS RICH WITH KNOWLEDGE.
THE YOUNG BOY'S FATHER WORKED IN A LOCAL LIBRARY.
THE FATHER WOULD BRING HIS SON TO THE LIBRARY AND THE SON WAS VERY HAPPY.
THE SON WOULD STAY UP LATE UNTIL 3 IN THE MORNING TO READ.
THE STORY SHOWS WHAT HAPPENED WHEN THE BOY GREW UP.
HE WAS THE FIRST TO GET A DEGREE IN HIS FAMILY AND WENT ON TO HAVE HIS OWN OFFICE WITH NAME TAG ON THE DOOR.
THE SON SHOWED HIS FATHER HIS ACCOMPLISHMENT.
THE FATHER WAS PROUD AND THE SON ENDED THE STORY BY SAYING HE DIDN'T KNOW WHAT HE WOULD BE IN HIS LIFE WITHOUT HAVING ACCESS TO BOOKS WHEN HE WAS YOUNG.
IN THE STORY, THERE IS A FAMILY WHO IS POOR.
THE DAD WORKS AND LIVES IN THE LIBRARY.
THE SON LOVES TO READ BOOKS IN THE LIBRARY AND WOULD STAY UP UNTIL 3 AM .
THE YOUNG BOY GREW UP TO BECOME A PROFESSOR .
HE SHOWED HIS FATHER HIS ACCOMPLISHMENTS AS HE WAS THE FIRST TO OBTAIN HIS DEGREE AND HAVE A CAREER.
THE BOY WHO GREW UP TO BE AN ACCOMPLISHED PROFESSOR WAS PROUD THAT HE HAD BOOKS IN HIS LIFE BY THE END OF THE STORY.
